            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>在 CES 2025 Nvidia 發佈最新 GeForce RTX 50 顯示卡系列，而各廠商微調的顯示卡產品也陸續推出。ROG(Republic of Gamers) 就發佈了最新 OC 版顯示卡 ROG Astral GeForce RTX 5090 OC Edition。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1288699" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250124105947-672x580.jpg" alt="" width="672" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250124105947-672x580.jpg 672w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250124105947.jpg 1043w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 672px" /></p><h2 data-pm-slice="1 1 []">創新冷卻系統</h2><p>全新 Quad-Fan Force 四風扇設計，大幅提升氣流與壓力達 20%，結合專利 Vapor Chamber 技術與相變 GPU 散熱墊，顯著降低 GPU 溫度。經過精心改良的散熱鰭片間距與 MaxContact 熱傳導技術，確保散熱效率提升 10%，讓裝置在高效運作時依然保持低溫穩定。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1288689 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250124110113-694x294.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="294" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250124110113-694x294.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250124110113-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1288696 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250124110245-694x393.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="393" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250124110245-694x393.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250124110245-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>強化結構與保護</h2><p>顯示卡採用全金屬鑄造框架與背板，搭配 GPU Guard 技術固定 GPU 四角，提供穩固結構與持久保護。PCB 防護塗層進一步抵禦濕氣、灰塵與雜質，減少短路風險。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1288688 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250124110027-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250124110027-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250124110027-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1288690 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250124110137-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250124110137-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250124110137.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1288691 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250124111523-694x355.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="355" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250124111523-694x355.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250124111523.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>
